{"lemma":"قَطَّةٍ","slug":"قَطَّةٍ","root":"ق.ط.ط","root_slug":"ق-ط-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ط-ط","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"قَطّ","root":"قطط","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adj","adv","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35841","n35858"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adv","gloss":"ever, never"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to carve"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut, to trim, to clip, to pare"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sharpen a nib, pencil"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"short and curly (of hair)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cat, tomcat","examples":[{"text":"القِطُّ يَلْعَبُ بِكُرَةٍ.","english":"The cat is playing with a ball."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of قَطَّ (qaṭṭa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Most likely to be onomatopoeic. See قَتَّ (qatta).\n\nCognate with Classical Syriac ܩܛܘ (qaṭṭu)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35841","headword_ar":"قَطَّهُ","root":"qT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~N","text_ar":"قَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a general sense: (M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning a hard thing, such as a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huq~p","text_ar":"حُقّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"box"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Lth, M, K,) and the like, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a good form,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fashion, like as a man cuts a reed upon a bone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoTiyTN","text_ar":"تَقْطِيطٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, [inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qT~Thu","text_ar":"قطّطهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cutting"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huq~ap","text_ar":"حُقَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and making"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~ahu","text_ar":"قَطَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut it breadthwise, across,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crosswise;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he so separated it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kh, S;) opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qad~ahu","text_ar":"قَدَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) which signifies he cut it in halves lengthwise, like as one cuts a strap or thong: (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqtT~hu","text_ar":"اقتطّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (M, K. *) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~a Alqalama","text_ar":"قَطَّ القَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) aor. as above, (K,) and so the inf. n., (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He nibbed the reed for writing; cut off its head breadthwise, across,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crosswise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~a AlbayoTaAru HaAfira Ald~aAb~api","text_ar":"قَطَّ البَيْطَارُ حَافِرَ الدَّابَّةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The farrier pared, and made even, the hoof of the beast of carriage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTTa Al$~aEaru","text_ar":"قَططَ الشَّعَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) with the reduplication made manifest, (S, M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~a","text_ar":"قَطَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaqaT~u","text_ar":"يَقَطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb, K,) and, of the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaquT~u","text_ar":"يَقُطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, [contr. to the general rule,] (Msb,) inf. n., of the former,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~N","text_ar":"قَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) which is extr., (M,) and of the latter, (M, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTaTN","text_ar":"قَطَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTaATapN","text_ar":"قَطَاطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The hair was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frizzled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very crisp, very curly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much twisted, and contracted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like that of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zanojiY~","text_ar":"زَنْجِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crisp, curly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twisted, and contracted, and short."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~a Als~iEoru","text_ar":"قَطَّ السِّعْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaqiT~u","text_ar":"يَقِطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) with kesr, (S, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaquT~u","text_ar":"يَقُطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb,) the verb being co-ordinate to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatala","text_ar":"قَتَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [contr. to the general rule,] (Msb) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~N","text_ar":"قَطٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quTuwTN","text_ar":"قُطُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quT~a","text_ar":"قُطَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm; (Fr, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The price was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and high:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) Sh thought this explanation to be wrong, and the meaning to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the price flagged;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but Az says, that in this he was mistaken. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaT~a A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"قَطَّ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~iEora","text_ar":"السِّعْرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God made the price to be,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"become, dear."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr. TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","Lth","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n35858","headword_ar":"قِطَّةٌ","root":"qT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of cutting"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing, such as the extremity of the nib of a writingreed]: see an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sin~N","text_ar":"سِنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(near the end of the paragraph)."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}